        "html": "<style>.slide-dark{width:1280px;height:720px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1a0a0a,#0f1a10);font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;color:#fff;padding:50px;position:relative}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:28px}.badge{background:rgba(239,68,68,.2);color:#f87171;padding:6px 16px;border-radius:20px;font-size:15px;font-weight:700}.logo{font-size:16px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.5)}.slide-title{font-size:34px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:24px}.myth-grid{display:flex;gap:20px;height:460px}.myth-col{flex:1;border-radius:20px;padding:32px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:space-between}.myth-col.old{background:rgba(239,68,68,.1);border:1px solid rgba(239,68,68,.3)}.myth-col.new{background:rgba(34,197,94,.1);border:1px solid rgba(34,197,94,.3)}.col-header{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:16px}.col-icon{font-size:44px}.col-label{font-size:28px;font-weight:700}.col-label.old{color:#f87171}.col-label.new{color:#4ade80}.col-body{font-size:26px;line-height:1.7;word-break:keep-all;flex:1}.col-source{font-size:18px;font-weight:700;padding:8px 16px;border-radius:12px;width:fit-content;margin-top:16px}.col-source.new{background:rgba(34,197,94,.15);color:#4ade80}.divider{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;width:40px;flex-shrink:0}.divider-arrow{font-size:48px;color:#fff;font-weight:900}.footer{position:absolute;bottom:20px;left:50px;right:50px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:14px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.3)}</style><div class='slide-dark'><div class='header'><span class='badge'>🔄 常識アップデート</span><span class='logo'>Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class='slide-title'>「人工甘味料」に関する常識の書き換え</div><div class='myth-grid'><div class='myth-col old'><div class='col-header'><div class='col-icon'>❌</div><div class='col-label old'>旧常識</div></div><div class='col-body'>カロリーゼロ<br>= 血糖値を上げない<br>= 太らない<br>= 糖尿病患者にも安全<br><br>「自由に使っていい甘味料」として推奨されてきた</div></div><div class='divider'><div class='divider-arrow'>→</div></div><div class='myth-col new'><div class='col-header'><div class='col-icon'>✅</div><div class='col-label new'>新常識（2022）</div></div><div class='col-body'>人工甘味料は腸内細菌叢を変化させ<br>インスリン抵抗性を悪化させる<br>可能性がある<br><br>特にサッカリン・スクラロースで<br>わずか2週間で変化が出現</div><div class='col-source new'>📄 Cell 2022, Suez et al.</div></div></div><div class='footer'><span>© Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
